Class Mediator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mediator.Mediator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMediator

    public final class Mediator
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMediator
    Mediator.java The class provides functionality for the Mediator design pattern. It is the class from where the Guis and complex gui elements are instantiated and through which they communicate with each other

    Jon
